features.各项水上娱乐项目皆具森林特色 , 被赋予森林主题 , 让人身处浩瀚森林又能享受到: forest-themed. It is like being in a vast forest close to the ocean.

features.以园林为特色的古镇 , 游严家花园等古典园林 , 坐船看小桥流水: The key feature of it is the garden. You can visit classical gardens such as Yanjia Garden, go on a boat ride and enjoy the flowing water.

features.贝聿铭设计的新馆清新雅致 , 欣赏镇馆之宝越窑秘色瓷莲花碗: The new and exquisitely elegant museum building of the Suzhou Museum designed by Ieoh Ming Pei is worth visiting and you can also enjoy the treasured Olive Green Lotus-Shaped Bowl.
features.苏州最大的购物中心 , 在金鸡湖边 , 边上就是东方之门: It is the biggest shopping mall in Suzhou. It is located just beside Jinji Lake and quite near the Gate of the Orient.
features.结合七部华谊兄弟原创电影 , 力邀国际国内知名电影美术师 , 突破传统设计手法: Based on the seven movies of the Huayi Brothers, the amusement park has invited famous movie artists to make groundbreaking designs to reproduce scenes from movies for visitors.
features.赏石湖胜景 , 看山水相依、峰峦重叠 , 领略苏州的山水文化底蕴: It's famous for Stone Lake's wonderful scenery and the endless rows of mountains and ridges. It's a great place to appreciate the mountain and water culture of Suzhou.
features.东方之门俗称 “ 秋裤 ”, 已经成为苏州网红打卡新地标 , 地处苏州工业园区: The Gate of the Orient, also commonly known as "long johns" because of its shape, has become a popular new landmark in Suzhou. It is located at the east end of the CBD axis of Suzhou Industrial Park.
features.欣赏苏州老城风貌 , 参观会馆等古迹 , 乘游船 , 拍摄美丽的夜景: enjoy the scenery of old Suzhou, visit the old guild hall and other historical sites, take a cruise on the river and take photos of the beautiful night scenery
features.千灯古镇 , 距今已有 2500 多年的历史 , 古镇白墙黑瓦 , 昆韵盎然。: Qiandeng Town has a history of more than 2500 years. You can enjoy its traditional buildings with white walls and black-tiled roofs and splendid scenery.
features.诚品书店是集文具、餐饮娱乐于一体的综合大楼: it integrates stationery, drink and food, and entertainment all in one building
features.西山是太湖中的第一大岛 , 岛上能看烟波飘渺的太湖湖景: Xishan Mountain is the biggest island in Taihu Lake. From the island, you can get a great view of the misty lake.
features.小桥流水与人家 , 双桥水巷摇橹船 , 还有沈万三的足迹待你寻访: It's famous for its many small bridges and winding waterways, the Twin Bridges, and the traditional Chinese riverboats. You can also walk in the footsteps of Shen Wansan.
features.松鹤楼、黄天源 , 能在苏州老字号里吃美食 ； 还能游览街名的来源玄妙观: Songhelou Restaurant, Huang Tianyuan and you can enjoy delicacies from time-honored Suzhou brands. You can also visit Xuanmiao Temple, the place that gave the street its name

features.赏石湖胜景 , 看山水相依、峰峦重叠 , 领略苏州的山水文化底蕴。: It's famous for Stone Lake's wonderful scenery and the endless rows of mountains and ridges. It's a great place to appreciate the mountain and water culture of Suzhou.

features.登苏州最大的山 , 在成片森林里深呼吸 , 寻访孙武等古代名人足迹。: climb the highest mountain in Suzhou, enjoy the fresh air of the forest and trace the footsteps of Sun Tzu and historical persons
features.苏州大学坐落于古城苏州 , 是国家 211 工程重点建设高校 , 其前身为创建于: Soochow University is located in the old town of Suzhou and is part of the national "211 Project". Its predecessor was the original Soochow University founded in 1900.
features.京剧样板戏 《 沙家浜 》 的发源地 , 访剧中场景 , 坐船深入芦苇荡。: the birthplace of the revolutionary Peking opera "Shajiabang". There you can visit the scene from the opera and take a boat amid reed marshes.
features.山体与江南园林风光相融 , 精致秀美 , 了解春秋旧事 , 观虎丘斜塔。: You can enjoy the beautiful scenery of mountains and Jiangnan gardens, learn more about the Spring and Autumn Period and visit the leaning Huqiu Pagoda.

features.范仲淹先祖归葬地 , 有浓郁的人文历史气息 ； 同时 , 山区的乱石路可以让您更: It is the burial place of the ancestors of Fan Zhongyan. The place is rich in cultural and historical aura. It's great fun climbing on the rocky roads in the area. Besides, you can enjoy red maple in mid-to-late November
features.欣赏千姿百态的海洋生物 , 观看丰富多彩的表演节目 , 感受缤纷海洋世界。: enjoy a variety of marine creatures, watch wonderful animal performances, and experience the colorful ocean world
features.京剧样板戏 《 沙家浜 》 的发源地 , 您可以在这里访剧中场景 , 坐船深入芦: the birthplace of the Peking Opera Shajiabang. Here, you can look at the settings from the opera and take a boat deep into the reeds.
features.千灯古镇 , 距今已有 2500 多年的历史 , 古镇白墙黑瓦 , 昆韵盎然: Qiandeng Town is an ancient town with a history of more than 2,500 years. There you can enjoy old buildings featuring black-tile roofs and white walls.
features.苏州四大名园之一 , 以假山闻名 , 数石狮子、钻石头迷宫乐趣无穷。: one of Suzhou's Four Famous Gardens, best known for its rock garden. When you're there you can count the stone lions and walk through the rock maze. There are loads of things to do.
features.苏州现存古老的园林 , 人少清静 , 复廊上的花窗非常精美。: one of the oldest gardens in Suzhou. It's very quiet and the lattice windows on the walls of the two-way corridor are very beautiful.
features.欣赏苏州老城风貌 , 参观会馆等古迹 , 乘游船 , 拍摄美丽的夜景。: You can enjoy the scenery of old Suzhou, visit the old guild hall and other historical sites, take a cruise on the river and take photos of the beautiful night scenery.
features.吃饭购物看电影都非常方便的地方 , 能叫得上名的品牌都集中了: It's a great place to shop, eat, or watch a movie. You can also various brands in the mall
features.吃饭购物看电影都非常方便的地方 , 能叫得上名的品牌都集中了。: Impression City Shopping Center is a great place to shop, eat, or watch a movie. You can also various brands in the mall.
features.以园林为特色的古镇 , 游严家花园等古典园林 , 坐船看小桥流水。: a water town featuring gardens. You can visit classical gardens such as Yanjia Garden, go on a boat ride and enjoy the flowing water.
features.中国四大名园之一 , 世界文化遗产。: a UNESCO World Heritage Site and one of China's Four Famous Gardens.
features.范仲淹先祖归葬地 , 走乱石路体验爬山乐趣 ,11 月中下旬赏红枫。: It's the burial place of the ancestors of Fan Zhongyan and it's great fun climbing on the rocky roads in the area. Besides, in mid-to-late November, you can view the beautiful enjoy red maple trees there.
features.西山是太湖中的第一大岛 , 岛上能看烟波飘渺的太湖湖景。: Xishan Mountain is the biggest island in Taihu Lake. From the island, you can get a great view of the misty lake.
features.诚品书店是集文具、餐饮娱乐于一体的综合大楼。: What is special about Eslite Bookstore is that it integrates stationery, drink and food, and entertainment all in one building.
features.千年名寺 , 诗句 “ 姑苏城外寒山寺 ” 的出处 , 来此撞钟、祈福。: This famous thousand-year temple is also the one in the poem "Beyond the Gusu District, from the Hanshan Temple". Tourists often strike the bell in the temple and pray for blessings.
features.以小巧精致著称的园林 , 了解布局的奥妙 , 夜游时欣赏曲艺表演。: It is a famous fine garden with traditional opera performances at night.
features.小家碧玉式的苏州园林 , 观赏园中三宝 : 冠云峰、楠木殿和鱼化石。: In the Suzhou-styled garden with humbleness, there are three treasures: Guanyun Peak, Nanmu Hall, and fish fossils.
features.这里曾是乾隆六下江南时走过的御道并有行宫遗址 ； 曾是越王勾践九年卧薪尝胆为吴王: It was once an imperial path passed by Emperor Qianlong when he visited the south of the Yangtze River for the sixth time and there was a palace site. It was once a place where King Goujian of Yue endured hardships for nine years and raised horses for King Wu.
features.爬山好去处 , 登山顶俯看苏州城景 , 在灵岩山寺拜佛祈福。: It is a good place to climb the mountain. At the top, we can overlook the scenery of Suzhou City, worship Buddha, and pray for blessings in Lingyan Mountain Temple.
features.攀登、坐船游览全国唯一的水陆城门盘门 , 走吴门桥 , 参观瑞光塔。: Climb or take a boat to visit the only water and land city gate in China — Pan Gate. Walk across the Wumen Bridge and visit the Ruiguang Tower.
features.圆融时代广场是集购物、餐饮、休闲、娱乐、商务、文化、旅游等诸多功能于一体的大规模: Yuanrong Times Square is a large-scale, comprehensive, modern, and high-quality commercial complex integrating shopping, catering, leisure, entertainment, business, culture, tourism, and other functions.
features.苏州最大的购物中心 , 在金鸡湖边 , 边上就是东方之门。: It is the biggest shopping mall in Suzhou. It is located just beside Jinji Lake and quite near the Gate of the Orient.
features.俗称的 “ 秋裤 ”—— 东方之门成为苏州网红打卡新地标 , 地处苏州工业园区: The Gate of the Orient, also commonly known as "long johns" because of its shape, has become a popular new landmark in Suzhou. It is located at the east end of the CBD axis of Suzhou Industrial Park.
features.环山路犹如玉带 , 可沿路欣赏太湖和精美的古建筑 , 品尝太湖三白。: The Huanshan Road, like a jade belt, enables the visitors to enjoy  Taihu Lake and exquisite ancient buildings along the road and they can taste the white fish, silverfish, and white shrimp of Taihu Lake.
features.漫步保存完整的古街区 , 看小桥流水古宅 , 逛文艺小店 , 吃美食。: Walk around the well-preserved ancient blocks, watch the bridges and flowing water, visit the literary and artistic shops, and eat delicious food.
